<article class="page prose">

<h1>every*where 2025</h1>

<p>The inaugural every*where: Adelaide Design Week ran <strong>20–24 August 2025</strong> — a city-wide, independently curated program of 19 events. Exhibitions, talks, open studios and installations across Kaurna/Adelaide, celebrating local design and the people who make it.</p>

<p class="program-link"><a href="{{ '/gallery/' | url }}">see the gallery →</a></p>

</article>

<section class="location-section" aria-label="All locations">

<figure class="location-map">
  <img src="{{ '/assets/images/program-2025/all-locations-map.jpg' | url }}" alt="Map of every*where 2025 event locations across Adelaide, 20–24 August 2025" loading="lazy">
  <figcaption><a href="{{ '/assets/all-locations-map-2025.pdf' | url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">download the full map (PDF) →</a></figcaption>
</figure>

</section>

<section class="program-section" aria-label="2025 program">

<h2 class="section-heading">the program</h2>

<ul class="program-grid program-grid--full">
{% for e in program2025 %}
  <li class="program-card">
    <div class="program-poster"><img src="{{ ('/assets/images/program-2025/' + e.image) | url }}" alt="{{ e.title }} poster" loading="lazy"></div>
    <h3 class="program-title">{{ e.title }}</h3>
    <p class="program-meta">{{ e.meta | safe }}</p>
    {% if e.sponsor %}<p class="program-sponsor">{{ e.sponsor }}</p>{% endif %}
    {% if e.description %}<p class="program-desc">{{ e.description | safe }}</p>{% endif %}
    {% if e.people %}
    <div class="program-people">
      <span class="program-people-label">{{ e.people.label }}</span>
      <ul class="program-people-list">
        {% for n in e.people.names %}<li>{{ n }}</li>{% endfor %}
      </ul>
    </div>
    {% endif %}
  </li>
{% endfor %}
</ul>

</section>

<article class="page prose">

<h2>the people</h2>

<p>every*where 2025 was made by a small, dedicated team and a wider community of contributors:</p>

<ul class="contributors">
{% for c in contributors2025 %}
  <li>{{ c.name }} <a href="{{ c.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">{{ c.handle }}</a></li>
{% endfor %}
</ul>

<p class="program-link"><a href="{{ '/team/' | url }}">meet the team →</a></p>

